OL,6,FAn 83-year-old woman who illegally
OL,7,Foperated as a loan shark has been
OL,8,Fordered to pay back #173,000.JTabitha
OL,9,FRichardson charged up to 40% in
OL,10,Finterest to people she lent money to
OL,11,Fand threatened victims saying she
OL,12,Fwould "come look for them".
OL,13,FRichardson, from , left one couple
OL,14,F"trapped in a cycle of debt" and
OL,15,Fhaving to pay back more than their
OL,16,Fmonthly income.JOfficers from the
OL,17,FWales Illegal Money Lending Unit
OL,18,F(WIMLU) visited the defendant on
OL,19,FAugust 30, 2022, after receiving
OL,20,Finformation about her illegal
OL,21,Factivities.
