OL,6,FShe had previously held a licence
OL,7,Fwhich allowed her to lend money
OL,8,Flegally but this had lapsed and she
OL,9,Fknowingly carried out her practices
OL,10,Fwhen unlicensed.JA search was carried
OL,11,Fout at Richardson's home in Nash Road
OL,12,Fand a safe was found in her garage.
OL,14,FShe initially claimed it contained
OL,15,Fproperty deeds and she had lost the
OL,16,Fkey, but a locksmith was called out to
OL,17,Fbreak open the safe, which was found
OL,18,Fto contain #6,550 in cash.JRichardson
OL,19,Flent a total of #126,000 while
OL,20,Funlicensed.
