OL,8,F#12,400.
OL,10,FThe female victim also received
OL,11,Fthreatening messages, with Richardson
OL,12,Ftexting her: "I don't want to come and
OL,13,Flook for you but you're not leaving me
OL,14,Fany other thing to do. Let's not fall
OL,15,Fout, we have known each other for a
OL,16,Flong time."JShe borrowed in the region
OL,17,Fof #46,300 and paid back #18,600 in
OL,18,Finterest.
